1153:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** * \details
1154:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  This function performs single scanning of one sensor in the widget configured
1155:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  by the CapSense_CSDSetupWidgetExt() function. It does the following
1156:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  tasks:
