1159:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *    3. Performs the Cmod pre-charging.
1160:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *    4. Starts single scanning.
